{
  "stem": "2581.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I don't know if they were Jewish or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Some were Jewish, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Some were Jewish, that's where the kapos-- some were homosexuals where they took young boys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They called them the pupils.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "One I came over to me, oh, would you want to move into my-- I said, of course I want to.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You'll have plenty of-- but I said, but I can't move without my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "When he heard that, another [NON-ENGLISH] in the face, he didn't need me anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember there was this man that came from Romania, he had oil wells, and he had this man with him, a friend or somebody to care on him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he kept sleeping with his legs curled, like that, and the other guy said, in Hungarian, and I understood it and to this very day, I sometimes-- another supposed to be a joke but doesn't always work, he kept saying [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Straighten out your legs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People didn't care about-- people died in the barracks next to you and you didn't even know who it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Finally it was going from bad to worse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This would have lasted another little while-- I can't give you-- no one would have come out from there except those that are walking around because when it became so bad that it became a hospital camp, they brought in Hungarian doctors.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, they were Jewish doctors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were no better than the Algerians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were mean.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm not saying because they were Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These people were mean.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They stole the food that even was for-- they looked healthy because they ate everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were doctors, they knew more than we did how to take care of ourselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But thank God it didn't last too long.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
